itects-9.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\" data-cfsrc=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/03/westminster-residence-batay-csorba-architects-9-810x1080.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAs described by the architects: “The simple project form is a composition of three dark monolithic figures, a low dark brick-clad volume, a heavy triangular stone-clad roof, and tall rectilinear dormers. The heavy roof hovers asymmetrically on top of the first floor, cantilevering the covered carport and side patio and producing an unsettling dynamic between the simple volumes. Similar in size and materiality, the dormers take on diametrically opposite stances in the project, with one grounding the west façade as it meets the ground, and the east dormer inexplicably cantilevered and hovering above the carport.”\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=571732\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-571732\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/03/westminster-residence-batay-csorba-architects-8-810x483.jpg\" alt=\"Modern kitchen with dark wood cabinets, a marble island with a built-in cooktop, and metal shelves. A vase with tall flowers is on the island, and a plant is on the right shelf.\" width=\"810\" height=\"483\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/03/westminster-residence-batay-csorba-architects-8-810x483.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/03/westminster-residence-batay-csorba-architects-8-800x478.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/03/westminster-residence-batay-csorba-architects-8-768x458.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/03/westminster-residence-batay-csorba-architects-8.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\" data-cfsrc=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/03/westminster-residence-batay-csorba-architects-8-810x483.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eDark stained walnut and heavy unfilled travertine reinforce the weight of the space, while white oak floors and soft lime-washed walls offer counterbalancing lightness. This material tension mirrors the formal tension between the asymmetrically balanced volumes – a heavy triangular stone roof that appears to float above the brick base, and dormers that simultaneously ground and hover. The architects also carefully considered how these materials would age. The natural patina that will develop on the rough terracotta shingles, hand-pressed brick, and raw galvanized steel will gradually harmonize with the spreading landscape.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=571737\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-571737\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/03/westminster-residence-batay-csorba-architects-17-810x608.jpg\" alt=\"Minimalist interior with two green chairs facing a beige wall and a brown alcove displaying decorative items. Neutral tones and wooden flooring create a modern, serene ambiance.\" width=\"810\" height=\"608\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/03/westminster-residence-batay-csorba-architects-17-810x608.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/03/westminster-residence-batay-csorba-architects-17-800x600.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/03/westminster-residence-batay-csorba-architects-17-768x576.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/03/westminster-residence-batay-csorba-architects-17.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\" data-cfsrc=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/03/westminster-residence-batay-csorba-architects-17-810x608.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=571738\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-571738\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/03/westminster-residence-batay-csorba-architects-20-810x1080.jpg\" alt=\"Modern interior with a marble table, a black chair, a framed abstract painting, beige curtains, and a window showing greenery outdoors.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1080\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/03/westminster-residence-batay-csorba-architects-20-810x1080.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/03/westminster-residence-batay-csorba-architects-20-800x1067.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/03/westminster-residence-batay-csorba-architects-20-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/03/westminster-residence-batay-csorba-architects-20-1152x1536.jpg 1152w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/03/westminster-residence-batay-csorba-architects-20.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\" data-cfsrc=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/03/westminster-residence-batay-csorba-architects-20-810x1080.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=571735\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-571735\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/03/westminster-residence-batay-csorba-architects-13-810x1080.jpg\" alt=\"Two green chairs and a small round table with a plant are arranged in front of sheer curtains in a bright, minimalist room with light wooden flooring and a sofa edge visible.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1080\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/03/westminster-residence-batay-csorba-architects-13-810x1080.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/03/westminster-residence-batay-csorba-architects-13-800x1067.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/03/westminster-residence-batay-csorba-architects-13-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/03/westminster-residence-batay-csorba-architects-13-1152x1536.jpg 1152w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/03/westminster-residence-batay-csorba-architects-13.jpg 1280w\"